      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint retains its original showroom shine with no scratches, chips, or swirl marks, and the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with all services performed on schedule and a complete history of records available. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
