    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks and feels great on the road? I'm parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs super smoothly, and has been well-loved over the years. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty is ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014I think you're going to love it!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
