      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. This example boasts sharp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and maintains a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Critical preventative maintenance is complete, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed bushings and a factory variable M differential lock. While the exterior shows honest wear from spirited use, the drivetrain is robust, having recently undergone a valve adjustment and cooling system refresh. A purist's configuration for the discerning driver.",
